snippet.title: Magic: The Gathering - Theros: Beyond Death Cinematic Trailer | The Game Awards 2019
snippet.description:
A new conflict has arisen in Magic: The Gathering, with 350 new cards coming soon to both tabletop and Arena with the Theros: Beyond Death card set.
